  <summary date="2017-04-27T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Veterans Crisis Line Improvement Act

This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to ensure that the first message a person hears upon calling the main telephone number of any VA medical facility allows the caller to choose to be quickly redirected to the Veterans Crisis Line without ending the call.</summary>
